jparsec.graph.chartRendering

Enum SkyRenderElement.MILKY_WAY_TEXTURE

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SkyRenderElement.MILKY_WAY_TEXTURE>

    SkyRenderElement

    public static enum SkyRenderElement.MILKY_WAY_TEXTURE
extends java.lang.Enum<SkyRenderElement.MILKY_WAY_TEXTURE>
    The set of textures for the milky way. All images except the optical one were taken from http://lambda.gsfc.nasa.gov/product/map/current/sos/7year/.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CO
      Use the CO (molecular clouds) map by Dame 2001.
      H_ALPHA
      Use the h-alpha image by Finkbeiner 2003.
      HI_21cm
      Use the 21cm (HI) line by Kalberla 2005.
      IRAS_100
      Use the IRAS map at 100 microns from Schlegel 1998.
      NO_TEXTURE
      Draw without texture.
      OPTICAL
      Use the optical image by Nick Risinger.
      WMAP
      Use the background microwave map from WMAP.
